{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/crawl-weibo-with-automa","result":{"data":{"blog":{"id":"f45a2074-4909-5ce1-836a-860a95485c1a","html":"<p>最近需要抓一点点微博的数据，于是又开始做爬虫的老行当了。不过这次抓的数据相对比较少，本来是觉得会很快，可惜还是因为种种原因多折腾了两个小时。这里对这部分工作做一个记录。</p>\n<p>我个人一直觉得爬虫是个很重要的东西，尤其是针对机器学习应用的研发，好的数据、新的数据、源源不断的新的数据是好的模型的前提。甚至不用做什么机器学习模型，仅仅从好的数据发掘的一些规则都很有帮助。所以，可以快速的抓数据、快速的抓各种各样的数据是一个很重要的能力。这里就不展开讲了，还是控制篇幅，以这次任务为主。</p>\n<h2 id=\"任务\" style=\"position:relative;\">任务<a href=\"#%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1\" aria-label=\"任务 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>从自己的微博首页或者随便一个主题下面抓点纯文本的微博数据，用于测试命名实体识别模型。</p>\n<h2 id=\"以前的方案\" style=\"position:relative;\">以前的方案<a href=\"#%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" aria-label=\"以前的方案 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>很久以前（大约还在读研究生的时候）那个时候的微博有一个移动版本，这个版本里面各种静态 html 非常好爬，所以难点基本就是发现 <code>m.weibo.com</code> 的存在...</p>\n<p>不过很遗憾，现在不论是 <code>weibo.com</code> 还是 <code>m.weibo.com</code> 都不再是纯 html 了，都会动态获取数据了，需要有 js 的运行时环境才能以比较自然的方式抓取数据，毕竟目前 weibo 的数据动态加载策略、参数啥的有点复杂了，去解析它更麻烦。</p>\n<h3 id=\"headless-chrome\" style=\"position:relative;\">Headless Chrome<a href=\"#headless-chrome\" aria-label=\"headless chrome permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>对于动态获取数据的页面来说，可以采用 headless browwser 配合 puppeteer 来模拟页面的操作以加载并获取数据。不过我觉得这样做很明显有这么几个缺点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>puppeteer 需要用 nodejs 编写，本身难度会比较大</li>\n<li>这种 headless 的脚本相对来说都挺脆弱的，页面展示稍微慢一点，或者元素稍微做了点变化，整个脚本就凉凉了，这个问题不是在有 puppeteer 之后采用的，在以前用 selenium 或者 casperjs 的年代也同样发生</li>\n</ol>\n<p>针对这个问题，我觉得有两个思路可以大大缓解：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>建立一个组件库，包含在浏览器实现各种行为的最佳实践，尽量规避自己写代码所引入的缺陷</li>\n<li>有一些类似于工作流的可视化界面，可以快速的建立一套爬取流程，虽然页面经常会发生变化，但由于我每次建立爬虫的成本大大降低了，所以我就不会那么在乎了</li>\n</ol>\n<p>而 webscraper 则恰恰提供了以上两个东西。</p>\n<h2 id=\"webscraper\" style=\"position:relative;\">webscraper<a href=\"#webscraper\" aria-label=\"webscraper permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://webscraper.io/\">webscraper</a> 是一个 chrome 扩展，其实它的内部依然是类似与 puppeteer 的东西，不过它做成了一个扩展，并提供了一些非常强大的封装，可以让你通过点点点就能实现一个数据爬虫的流程。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/c3611/webscraper-screenshot.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"webscraper screenshot\"\n        title=\"webscraper screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/5a190/webscraper-screenshot.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/772e8/webscraper-screenshot.png 200w,\n/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/e17e5/webscraper-screenshot.png 400w,\n/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/5a190/webscraper-screenshot.png 800w,\n/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/c1b63/webscraper-screenshot.png 1200w,\n/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/29007/webscraper-screenshot.png 1600w,\n/static/4d9649aee2db25721942a1ede588d6f1/c3611/webscraper-screenshot.png 2992w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>封装程度高到如下的样子：</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-提供丰富的组件对应不同的抓取模式\" style=\"position:relative;\">1. 提供丰富的组件，对应不同的抓取模式<a href=\"#1-%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%93%E5%8F%96%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"1 提供丰富的组件对应不同的抓取模式 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/55681/webscraper-element-type.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"webscraper element type\"\n        title=\"webscraper element type\"\n        src=\"/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/5a190/webscraper-element-type.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/772e8/webscraper-element-type.png 200w,\n/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/e17e5/webscraper-element-type.png 400w,\n/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/5a190/webscraper-element-type.png 800w,\n/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/c1b63/webscraper-element-type.png 1200w,\n/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/29007/webscraper-element-type.png 1600w,\n/static/664504027740f16a14fc23fa13769482/55681/webscraper-element-type.png 2062w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>包括：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>滚动到底部的瀑布加载</li>\n<li>各种类型的分页</li>\n<li>表格</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"2-内置-element-selector-可以在可视化界面完成页面元素的筛选\" style=\"position:relative;\">2. 内置 element selector 可以在可视化界面完成页面元素的筛选<a href=\"#2-%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE-element-selector-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E5%8C%96%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%9B%E9%80%89\" aria-label=\"2 内置 element selector 可以在可视化界面完成页面元素的筛选 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/36909/element-selector.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"element selector\"\n        title=\"element selector\"\n        src=\"/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/5a190/element-selector.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/772e8/element-selector.png 200w,\n/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/e17e5/element-selector.png 400w,\n/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/5a190/element-selector.png 800w,\n/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/c1b63/element-selector.png 1200w,\n/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/29007/element-selector.png 1600w,\n/static/89ff37cb4b5f872602736ec3f3ff5c6b/36909/element-selector.png 2772w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>通过点点点，就能简历一个 css selector 来定位所要抓取的 html 元素路径。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-建立层级数据结构\" style=\"position:relative;\">3. 建立层级数据结构<a href=\"#3-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\" aria-label=\"3 建立层级数据结构 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>在步骤 2 定位了想要抓取的具体数据后，可以在该数据上建立层级结构，标记具体想要抓取的数据结构，非常方便数据的结构化。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/45662/webscraper-structure.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"webscraper structure\"\n        title=\"webscraper structure\"\n        src=\"/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/5a190/webscraper-structure.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/772e8/webscraper-structure.png 200w,\n/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/e17e5/webscraper-structure.png 400w,\n/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/5a190/webscraper-structure.png 800w,\n/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/c1b63/webscraper-structure.png 1200w,\n/static/f2ca49df475a10844e372ff6e61f8ff7/45662/webscraper-structure.png 1410w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>有关这个东西有一个 <a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/web-scraper/\">卤蛋工作室</a> 很详细的对它做了系列教程，感兴趣的话推荐一看，我这里就简单说说。不过很遗憾，这个东西在如今的微博也不太能用了。虽然现在的微博很符合它所提供的「滚动到底部」的抓取模式，但目前的微博出于性能的考虑，对自己的这个微博列表做了元素重用，导致不论怎么滚动，最多就只有这么多个元素了。那么套用 webscraper 的「滚动到底部」就只能获取这么多个微博而已了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/7f2ab/dynamic-content-refresh.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dynamic content refresh\"\n        title=\"dynamic content refresh\"\n        src=\"/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/5a190/dynamic-content-refresh.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/772e8/dynamic-content-refresh.png 200w,\n/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/e17e5/dynamic-content-refresh.png 400w,\n/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/5a190/dynamic-content-refresh.png 800w,\n/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/c1b63/dynamic-content-refresh.png 1200w,\n/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/29007/dynamic-content-refresh.png 1600w,\n/static/f1de1475dcdda46d6c56cffd55fd3180/7f2ab/dynamic-content-refresh.png 2236w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"automa\" style=\"position:relative;\">Automa<a href=\"#automa\" aria-label=\"automa permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>Automa 也是一个 chrome 的扩展，相对于 webscraper 只用来做爬虫，automa 可以用来做各种流程自动化的东西，比 webscraper 灵活不少。除此之外，很多思路和 webscraper 一脉相承。简单看了看教程我就做出来如下一个流程：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/4b7ac/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"weibo scrape in automa\"\n        title=\"weibo scrape in automa\"\n        src=\"/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/5a190/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/772e8/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png 200w,\n/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/e17e5/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png 400w,\n/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/5a190/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png 800w,\n/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/c1b63/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png 1200w,\n/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/29007/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png 1600w,\n/static/7539ef465eb1bc02d46ac6cfd52d617b/4b7ac/weibo-scrape-in-automa.png 3444w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>其中的 <code>javascript code</code> 内容如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">inViewport</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">element</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> html <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> rect <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getBoundingClientRect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>rect <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n    rect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bottom <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n    rect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>right <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> \n    rect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>left <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> html<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientWidth <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n    rect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>top <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> html<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> elements <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"article\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  elements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">inViewport</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.detail_wbtext_4CRf9'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerText<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">automaNextBlock</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">text</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> text <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>和 webscraper 一直滚动到满意的个数的元素后再开始解析数据不同，我做的 automa 的流程是每次滚动一点点页面，然后就获取当前视图中的微博元素并把其内容存下来。而获取当前视图的元素就是用的上面的 <code>javascript code</code> 了。</p>\n<p>\n\t\t<video\n\t\t\tsrc=/videos/automa-scrape-weibo.mp4\n\t\t\twidth=\"1200\"\n\t\t\theight=\"auto\"\n\t\t\tpreload=\"auto\"\n\t\t\tmuted=\"false\"\n\t\t\ttitle=\"/videos/automa-scrape-weibo.mp4\"\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tplaysinline\n\t\t\tcontrols\n\t\t\t\n\t\t></video>\n\t</p>\n<h2 id=\"小结\" style=\"position:relative;\">小结<a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"小结 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>Automa 相对 webscraper 来说更加灵活，可以更加灵活的定制自己的抓取流程，后续可能还会有其他场景的使用吧。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1\">任务</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\">以前的方案</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#headless-chrome\">Headless Chrome</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#webscraper\">webscraper</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%93%E5%8F%96%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\">1. 提供丰富的组件，对应不同的抓取模式</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE-element-selector-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E5%8C%96%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%9B%E9%80%89\">2. 内置 element selector 可以在可视化界面完成页面元素的筛选</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\">3. 建立层级数据结构</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#automa\">Automa</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\">小结</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"使用 Automa 抓取少量微博数据","date":"April 14, 2022","tags":["automa","chrome","crawler"]},"excerpt":"最近需要抓一点点微博的数据，于是又开始做爬虫的老行当了。不过这次抓的数据相对比较少，本来是觉得会很…"}},"pageContext":{"id":"f45a2074-4909-5ce1-836a-860a95485c1a"}},"staticQueryHashes":["4202924991"]}